Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——CQ1——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:24.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Lanterns make red gate red more fantastically
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:35.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Wooden clogs play the sound in the deep tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:51.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Sliver moon Shines and laughs proudly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:01:02.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}pale stars just keep silence in the robe of night
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Shaved ice in every color of the rainbow
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}It's melting swiftly and quickly in the summer sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:14.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\be3}Earworm has been around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:21.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be3}Everything of routine, hang out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:27.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\be3}conversation I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:02:03.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}You have vanished from me like a mirage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:09.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Where have you been midday sun worked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:14.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I think I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:23.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\be3}That is never happened before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:35.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\be3}I thought I will see you tomorrow
Comment: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:35.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I thought I'll see you again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:24.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}燈火搖曳 映紅了鳥居的朱頂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:35.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}梆啷作響 是木屐嬉鬧的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:51.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}青紗帳外 幾點淡藍的星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:01:02.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}舉目四顧 月光清冷透剔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,五顏六色 手中冰棒亮晶晶
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,融解消散 紙風車舞在風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:27.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總有聲音 在耳畔揮之不去 原來是你 笑聲如銀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:02:03.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}涼夜如水 安撫燥熱的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:14.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你的背影 已朦朧在我眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:35.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}明日定能再相會 我深信不疑
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——CQ2——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I don't need too much stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Want to live simply
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:39.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I'm looking for the faith so have just a Bible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Why don't we be easy going
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}That's OK Happy go Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}What is a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}You say "NO" always
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:11.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I don't care stereotyped and everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}I got something day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Ready whatever come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Everybody linving life today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:39.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}"Take no thought for the morrow"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}That's OK just like us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Let's live life today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}sign for beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}That's true time will tell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Quickly pocketed the bible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我不需要太多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}只想活的簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:39.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我尋求信仰 所以一本聖經在手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}為何我們不能從容不迫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沒什麼不行 隨遇而安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}為何總是說「不」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:11.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我不在乎陳規和平凡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}每天我都有所得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}為明天會來的一切做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}每個人都活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:39.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沒人關註明天會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沒關係 我們都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}讓我們活在當下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}標註著開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沒錯 時間會證明一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}快收起聖經
